intent.user_query: What is the distribution of service ticket resolution times (e.g., how many tickets are resolved within 1 day, 1 week, 1 month)?

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT CASE WHEN ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 1 THEN 'Within 1 Day' WHEN ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 7 THEN 'Within 1 Week' WHEN ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 30 THEN 'Within 1 Month' ELSE 'Over 1 Month' END AS ResolutionTime, COUNT(*) AS NumberOfTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets WHERE ResolutionDate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 2 DESC;

arguments.sql: SELECT CASE WHEN ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 1 THEN 'Within 1 Day' WHEN ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 7 THEN 'Within 1 Week' WHEN ResolutionDate - TicketDate <= 30 THEN 'Within 1 Month' ELSE 'Over 1 Month' END AS ResolutionTime, COUNT(*) AS NumberOfTickets FROM fitness_db.ServiceTickets WHERE ResolutionDate IS NOT NULL GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 2 DESC;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
